# Google Maps API keys — required for the Map screen (US-6) to render tiles in a
# dev or standalone build. Expo Go does not provide a Maps key, so the map is
# blank there; a dev build with a key shows real tiles + your bed/nursery markers.
#
# Create restricted keys in Google Cloud Console (Maps SDK for Android / iOS):
#   - Android: restrict to package  edu.psu.sweng888.group4.gardenguard  + your SHA-1
#   - iOS:     restrict to bundle id edu.psu.sweng888.group4.gardenguard
#
# Copy this file to `.env` (gitignored) and fill in, then: npx expo run:android
GOOGLE_MAPS_ANDROID_API_KEY=
GOOGLE_MAPS_IOS_API_KEY=
